Blurb::
Evidence theory with evidence measures computed with local optimization methods
Description::
<b> See the topic page \ref topics-evidence_theory for important
background information and usage notes </b>

Two local optimization methods 
are available: \c sqp (sequential quadratic programming or \c nip
(nonlinear interior point method). 

